						</a>
					</div>

				<span class="prof">
						Project Manager в <a class="company" href="https://jobs.dou.ua/companies/io/" target="_blank"><span class="company-favicon" style="background: url(https://s.dou.ua/img/static/favicons/16_wYkAidc.png) no-repeat;">IO Technologies</span></a>
